'''阿斯玛·法瓦兹·艾尔-阿克拉斯·阿萨德'''（{{lang-ar|<big>أسماء الأسد</big>}}），原名阿斯玛·法瓦兹·艾尔-阿克拉斯（{{lang-ar|<big>أسماء فواز الأخرس</big>}}，{{bd|1975年|8月11日|}}），是一名[[英国|英国]]出生的[[叙利亚人|叙利亚人]]，2000年12月与[[叙利亚|叙利亚]]总统[[巴沙尔·阿萨德|巴沙尔·阿萨德]]结婚<ref>[http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/syria/8503481/Is-Asma-Assad-in-London.html Is Asma Assad in London?] {{Wayback|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/syria/8503481/Is-Asma-Assad-in-London.html |date=20110611144310 }}[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]], By Nabila Ramdani, 10 May 2011</ref>。之前她是一名银行投资家。

==早年==
[[Image:Asma_al-Assad_and_Marisa_Leticia.jpg|thumb]]
她在伦敦[[伊靈區|伊靈區]]的[[阿克頓_(倫敦)|阿克頓地区]]长大，在当地的一所[[英国国教会|英国国教会]]学校上学<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/1630134.stm |title=The road to Damascus (all the way from Acton) |work=BBC News |date=31 October 2001 |accessdate=1 April 2011 |archive-date=2008-04-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080406124345/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/1630134.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1996年获得[[伦敦国王学院|伦敦国王学院]]的[[计算机科学|计算机科学]]学士与[[法语文学|法语文学]]学位<ref>{{cite news |first=Oliver |last=Harvey |url=http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/features/2514525/Sexy-Brit-bringing-Syria-in-from-the-cold.html |title=Sexy Brit bringing Syria in from the cold |publisher=The Sun |date=3 July 2009 |accessdate=26 March 2011 |archive-date=2012-03-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120318114831/http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/features/2514525/Sexy-Brit-bringing-Syria-in-from-the-cold.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

毕业后，她在[[德意志银行|德意志银行]]负责[[欧洲|欧洲]]和[[远东|远东]]事务的一个资金管理部门工作。1998年她加入投资银行——[[摩根大通#J.P.摩根公司|J.P.摩根公司]]负责处理[[并购|并购]]业务{{Citation needed|date=November 2011}}。

===家庭===
她的父亲是伦敦 ''Cromwell Hospital'' 的[[心脏病|心脏病]]专家Fawaz Akhras，母亲是退休的外交官Sahar Otri al-Akhras。她父母都是出身于[[霍姆斯_(叙利亚)|霍姆斯]]的叙利亚裔[[逊尼派|逊尼派]]穆斯林<ref name=Bar_S.380/><ref>{{cite news|last=Bar'el|first=Zvi|title=In Syria, the army's loyalty to Assad runs deep|url=http://www.haaretz.com/print-edition/features/in-syria-the-army-s-loyalty-to-assad-runs-deep-1.358310|accessdate=17 July 2011|newspaper=Haaretz|date=27 April 2011|archive-date=2011-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110522002113/http://www.haaretz.com/print-edition/features/in-syria-the-army-s-loyalty-to-assad-runs-deep-1.358310|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==个人生活==
[[File:Bashar_and_Asmaa_al-Assad_in_Moscow.jpg|thumb]]]]
她在一次到叙利亚度假时认识了巴沙尔<ref>[http://www.newstatesman.com/middle-east/2011/05/lady-asma-syria-assad-london Asma al-Assad is no reformer] {{Wayback|url=http://www.newstatesman.com/middle-east/2011/05/lady-asma-syria-assad-london |date=20111218221210 }}[[New_Statesman|New Statesman]], Nabila Ramdani, Published 26 May 2011</ref>。巴沙尔当上总统后，她于2000年11月正式移民成为叙利亚人，12月与巴沙尔结婚。育有三个子女：Hafez，Zein和Karim<ref name=Bar_S.380>{{cite journal|last=Bar|first=Shmuel|title=Bashar's Syria: The Regime and its Strategic Worldview|journal=Comparative Strategy|year=2006|volume=25|pages=380|url=http://www.herzliyaconference.org/_Uploads/2590Bashars.pdf|accessdate=15 May 2011|archive-date=2011-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110723214138/http://www.herzliyaconference.org/_Uploads/2590Bashars.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2011年5月10日，一个外交文件报道说她已经带三个孩子出国以躲避[[叙利亚内战|叙利亚内战]]，现在居住于伦敦<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/syria/8503481/Is-Asma-Assad-in-London.html |title=Is Asma Assad in London? |work=The Telegraph |first=Nabila |last=Ramdani |date=10 May 2011 |accessdate=11 May 2011 |archive-date=2011-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110611144310/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/syria/8503481/Is-Asma-Assad-in-London.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。叙利亚驻英国大使Sami Khiyami否认这个报道<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.jpost.com/Headlines/Article.aspx?id=220196 |title=Syrian ambassador: Asma Assad did not escape to London |publisher=The Jerusalem Post |date=12 May 2011 |accessdate=20 May 2011 |archive-date=2012-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023163937/http://www.jpost.com/Headlines/Article.aspx?id=220196 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2011年6月30日，她被拍到在[[大马士革|大马士革]]问候支持政府的示威民众<ref name=Gulfnews>{{cite news|title=Al Assad sacks governor of Syria flashpoint city|url=http://gulfnews.com/news/region/syria/al-assad-sacks-governor-of-syria-flashpoint-city-1.831577|accessdate=11 August 2011|newspaper=Gulf News|date=2 July 2011|archive-date=2012-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120116234815/http://gulfnews.com/news/region/syria/al-assad-sacks-governor-of-syria-flashpoint-city-1.831577|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2021年3月8日，阿斯玛确诊感染COVID-19病毒<ref>{{cite news |title=叙利亚总统巴沙尔及其夫人确诊感染新冠病毒 |url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/photo/2021-03/09/c_1127188743.htm}}</ref>。

